messages.subject: Is someone missing a set of Thinking Sticks?

messages.messageBody:
I have misplaced a Thinking Sticks order. I think it was just a check in a
small envelope with a "thinking sticks" notation. I know where it used to be,
and I've had faith it will turn up, but I'm losing faith.

If it was someone here or if somone here has a friend who ordered some
lately, please write to me!

Very sorry. (And now that I've done this, the envelope will probably turn up
in an obvious place.)

Sandra
